  user_input {
    user_response: "Build me a react app with screens that look like this. You can hotlink images from the html. for the layout, using vanilla CSS (or something cool liks scss - DO NOT USE INLINE STYLES) for responsive styling. Use typescript for all component props and ensure a clean, modular folder structure. Also, implement dark/light mode support using CSS variables. and ensure proper accessibility standards are met throughout the UI components. Finally, add smooth transitions for all interactive elements.\n\ncreate a UI for my portfolio, i want clean/decent UI with some clean sroll animatioon effect and with consistent fonts/colors and a button that says something like \"View My Resume\" on clicking this button a pdf viewer should pop up like a modal with a download button and close button. refer my resume (attached file) to make a UI focusing/highlighting my skills and projects.\n\n\n\nMy ideal portfolio links to get UI inspiration:\n\nhttps://brittanychiang.com/\n\nhttps://www.sarahdayan.com/\n\nhttps://bimaindra.com/\n\n\n\n\n\nI want to add a toggle between light and dark mode.\n\n\n\nMy github: https://github.com/SyedShamaan2000/\n\nMy linkendIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/syed-shamaan-hussaini\n\nMy email: syedshamaan14@gmail.com\n\n"
    items {
      text: "Build me a react app with screens that look like this. You can hotlink images from the html. for the layout, using vanilla CSS (or something cool liks scss - DO NOT USE INLINE STYLES) for responsive styling. Use typescript for all component props and ensure a clean, modular folder structure. Also, implement dark/light mode support using CSS variables. and ensure proper accessibility standards are met throughout the UI components. Finally, add smooth transitions for all interactive elements.\n\ncreate a UI for my portfolio, i want clean/decent UI with some clean sroll animatioon effect and with consistent fonts/colors and a button that says something like \"View My Resume\" on clicking this button a pdf viewer should pop up like a modal with a download button and close button. refer my resume (attached file) to make a UI focusing/highlighting my skills and projects.\n\n\n\nMy ideal portfolio links to get UI inspiration:\n\nhttps://brittanychiang.com/\n\nhttps://www.sarahdayan.com/\n\nhttps://bimaindra.com/\n\n\n\n\n\nI want to add a toggle between light and dark mode.\n\n\n\nMy github: https://github.com/SyedShamaan2000/\n\nMy linkendIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/syed-shamaan-hussaini\n\nMy email: syedshamaan14@gmail.com\n\n"
