  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Confirming Build Success**\n\nI\'m pleased to report the applet compiled without error! I\'m now cross-referencing all user requests, starting with ensuring the React app mirrors the provided snapshot image\'s styling exactly. That includes dark backgrounds, emerald accents, the positioning of the headshot, and layout of the elements.\n\n\n**Confirming Code Compliance**\n\nI\'m happy to announce the avatar, and project images are all hotlinked directly from the HTML, which simplifies asset management. Further, CSS, SCSS, and responsive styling are implemented without inline styles, using theme mappings, variables and Tailwind classes. I\'ve also verified TypeScript usage for all component props, with a modular folder structure. Data is neatly grouped in `/src/data.ts` and components are separated for improved reusability.\n\n\n**Implementing UI Enhancements**\n\nI\'ve successfully implemented dark/light mode with CSS variables, offering a deep navy-slate for dark mode and an elegant slate-light feel for light mode. Accessibility standards are also met. I\'ve ensured contrast ratios, alt text, semantic markup and logical text groupings. Transitions are in place for all interactive elements, and custom Framer Motion animations have been added. I also worked on a \"View My Resume\" button that will show a PDF viewer modal.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have designed and built a minimalist, technical developer portfolio for **Peerzada Syed Shamaan Hussaini** that matches your requested layout, aesthetic quality, and interaction designs. \n\nHere is an overview of the visual style and interactive modules implemented:\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual Theme & Style\n*   **Default \"Quietly Confident\" Theme**: Set a deep navy-slate dark background and typography system using **Space Grotesk** for display headers paired with **Inter** for body text and **JetBrains Mono** for monospaced technical labels.\n*   **Dual-Theme Mode (CSS Variables)**:\n    *   **Dark Mode**: Implemented vibrant, futuristic Emerald-Green (`#5dd3b3`) and Electric Blue (`#38bdf8`) accents.\n    *   **Light Mode**: Transitioned to an elegant off-white canvas with high-contrast, WCAG AA/AAA-accessible deep teal (`#0f766e`) accents.\n*   **No Inline Styles**: All layout styling was executed cleanly using utility-mapped CSS custom variables inside `/src/index.css` via Tailwind CSS v4.\n\n### \360\237\222\274 Portfolio Sections\n1.  **Top Navigation Bar**: Frozen at the top of the interface with an elegant glassmorphism blur and smooth-scroll indicators that update dynamically based on the current viewport offset. Features a responsive slide-down mobile nav menu.\n2.  **Display Hero**: Showcases a massive geometric display header, responsive CTA targets, and a professional grayscaled avatar. On mouse hover, the avatar shifts from grayscale to full color, showing subtle code snippet overlays and visual depth.\n3.  **Technical Stack (\"About\")**: Structured as a bento-style capabilities catalog that clusters skills into custom groups with micro-hover highlights.\n4.  **Professional Timeline (\"Experience\")**: Outlines Shamaan\'s roles as a Full Stack Developer at **Sakesh InfoTech** and Remote Developer Intern at **CodeClause**, detailed with bullet parameters and tags.\n5.  **Interactive Showroom (\"Projects\")**: Highlights **BudgetBuddy**, **AI-ChatLingo**, and **TaskTrackr** using actual hotlinked digital graphics. Clicking on any project card opens an immersive **Deep-Dive details window** highlighting the Technical Challenge, Solutions, and Performance Outcomes.\n6.  **Contact Flow**: Features an interactive message form with loading wheels, local validation, and successful simulated send alerts, beside a direct email mailto trigger.\n\n### \360\237\223\204 Simulated A4 PDF Resume Viewer Modal\n*   **Authentic Document View**: Clicking the **\"View My Resume\"** button opens a full-screen blurred viewport displaying Shamaan\'s resume mapped to A4 proportions. \n*   **Complete Resum\303\251 Data**: Includes Sakesh InfoTech outcomes, CodeClause tasks, academic CGPAs, and achievements like the MetLife Hackathon.\n*   **Client-Side Download Trigger**: Clicking the download button automatically compiles and prompts a download of Shamaan\'s formatted resume as a raw `.txt` document.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 3
      nanos: 695813504
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
